verbose_text: The right side of XREF_FIG illustrates that the anti-senescence effect of let-7g may be mediated by suppressing the oxLDL-LOX-1 pathway, while the left side indicates that let-7g may also suppress IGF1 signaling to exert the anti-senescence effect.
